; Test bal with a periodic transaction defined but not activated
; Note: without --budget, the periodic transaction is ignored; only the
; real transaction is reflected in the output

~ Monthly
    Expenses:Food    $300.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Checking

test bal
            $-100.00  Assets:Checking
             $100.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
